<p>â€¦with open source <a href="https://certification.oshwa.org/us000105.html">friction adjusters</a>â€¦</p>

<p><img src="/images/hummingbird_hammocks_friction_adjusters_400_px.png" alt="Friction Adjusters" /></p>

<p><em>Image courtesy Hummingbird Hammocks</em></p>

